Apparently, the De Simplex Magicae had some sort of safety feature implemented which transformed the destroyed pages back into a magic book when Elvenhair and Brandock attempted to conserve the remaining pages. Now it has an introduction in a rune language no one speaks anymore and is seemingly empty. Elvenhair believes the spells have to be added back by a mage of high enough expertise, but to know for sure they need to decipher the pages covered in Ruathlek runes.~
