@10071  = ~Brandock's Half-Ogre Troubles

Brandock is now ready to use his ability to shapeshift into a half-ogre.~
@10072  = ~Brandock's Half-Ogre Troubles

Brandock is no longer afraid to use his ability to shapeshift into a half-ogre.~
